## THE CLOSING (Actually)

6 years. One idea, stated many ways. The ways multiply. The idea stays.

You could put this system file in an AI and generate content. The content would sound like me. It would not be me. The delta between “sounds like” and “is” is worth understanding. The delta is experience. The delta is the years. The delta is the 50,796 tweets and what they taught, which cannot be fully captured in a file, which is why the file says the person is the moat, which is why I keep writing.

The file is the map. The person is the territory.

Never confuse the map for the territory.

(I’ll remind you of this next week. And the week after. And probably the week after that. It’ll still be true. We’ll arrive at the same place again. That’s the journey. This is the compass.)

